      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Prompt : Codice ns. banca o c/c postale                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-cod-cbp-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      28                   to   v-car                  .
           move      08                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           if        rr-tad-drc           =    1840
                     move  "Codice nostro C/C Postale  :"
